Usage: feelings [<prefix>]
       feelings guild [<guild>] [<prefix>]

Lists standard feelings and the guild feelings currently available to you.
The optional prefix limits the results by name. Guild listings never reveal
emotes belonging to guilds you cannot currently use.

Examples:
  feelings grin
  feelings guild
  feelings guild Street_Samurai
  feelings guild Street_Samurai jack

See also: emotes, emoteapropos, guild emotes, semote
